Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.75,0:01:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，合體準備，好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.39,0:01:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧，良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.78,0:01:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5、4、3、2、1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.92,0:01:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,激光射線同步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.99,0:01:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5、4、GUNDAM B部件投下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核心戰鬥機變形、合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於逃出White Base的阿姆羅來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.68,0:02:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從未經歷過如此的「訓練」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.95,0:02:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰艦格瓦金於月球ZION公國的\N前線基地格拉納達出航了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.44,0:02:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是薩比家的長女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.71,0:02:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是ZION軍宇宙攻擊軍總司令\N基西莉亞·薩比少將的旗艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.51,0:02:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基西莉亞下訪了對於地球聯邦軍以及ZION軍\N最重要的資源開發地馬·克貝處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.73,0:02:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭朝著與White Base沒關係的方向進行著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『灼熱的阿薩姆導引器』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.34,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果今次阿姆羅回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應如何是好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臨陣退縮的人當然要處死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你胡說，他不會的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果以軍法來說是會判死刑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅和我們作戰至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎可如此無情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是說有必要才會如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別亂說，雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了！芙勞·波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在明白阿姆羅離開的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不會找他回來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了！好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳別太認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們始終不是正式軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又怎會這樣對待阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是良...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也不可以任由阿姆羅胡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...事實他也有不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，那妳認為他對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是明白妳意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐...和我們一起去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不成！我不是去玩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.64,0:05:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那妳去那裏呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去找阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為芙勞·波可帶阿姆羅回來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要看時間是否配合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.85,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來阿姆羅哥是VSOP...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,VSOP？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是重要人物啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.68,0:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說錯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會亂來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅會平安的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找他回來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有嚇到你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知你們最關心的只是GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你誤會了，大家說會原諒你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原諒我？是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱說臨陣退縮是會判死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.44,0:08:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來妳來的目的只是說這一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.11,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦上的大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是需要阿姆羅的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又要逃走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.78,0:08:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是沒信心讓大家認同自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才不想回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳又怎會知道我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們到底在幹什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要等芙勞·波回來才可出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.82,0:08:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下地址不便成了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說中亞細亞百中立區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但仍有很多ZION軍存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給發現便麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅這傢伙回來的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2時方向有金屬反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何突然停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.52,0:09:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.96,0:09:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去不便成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一噸的2公克含量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我預測沒錯 這礦場的品質很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以再發堀5個這樣的礦場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可必勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.65,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是什麼情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.85,0:09:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種礦場不可落入聯邦軍手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要進一步統治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.36,0:10:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便要設法打勝這場仗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點我是明白的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離此50公里的北方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有一個差不多的礦場存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.07,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我便照你所申請的送來應用吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是ZION軍的採礦基地！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.85,0:10:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於給我找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！到底有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我也沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面有個ZION的採礦基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！被發現便不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別小覷我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有如此愚蠢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，還是和母艦聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！若給發現訊息就對我們不利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不如回母艦報訊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就留此監視一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.98,0:10:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我明白了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經3個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥嘉，有消息吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼也未有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被敵軍發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會沒命的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快小心監視探測器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想阿姆羅不會投誠ZION軍吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有可能的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿GUNDAM當禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他便可做大英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.11,0:11:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，他的投誠者呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！如果這樣可不是說笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.99,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷比爾將軍所說敖德薩計劃的礦山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎一個機動戰士也沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以去毀滅它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果用GUNDAM毀滅了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍不用移動到此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不用再聽隊長和米萊的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.82,0:12:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基希莉亞大人，請來這邊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要趕回去立即通知大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被發現也沒法了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞沙姆，快準備出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬·克貝，你怎會查不出有敵軍的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要如何交待！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基希莉亞將軍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞沙姆試驗的性能十分良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去駕駛它吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.35,0:12:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳放心吧！將軍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.33,0:13:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以親眼見識聯邦的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對日後的作戰會更有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在後面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣便完了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從卡爾瑪的資料上看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比普通機動戰士的性能高很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬·克貝上校，你要加倍小心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在上面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在上面呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.78,0:15:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射衝擊熱炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表面溫度有4仟度？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是剛才那像沙的東西所引起的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.75,0:16:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請注意\N熱能下降98%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.76,0:16:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放出了98%那還可動？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說那邊的礦山是基地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真難以置信！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這地點有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和雷比爾將軍的資料有所出入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是真的 我也親眼看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很大的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之不能不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.78,0:17:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去看看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基希莉亞將軍，我們成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上我們對機動戰士的研究是較強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來放熱磁場減弱了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快毀滅它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷卻裝置開動，熱量下降！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可以動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.07,0:17:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被避開了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是ZAKU早就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再試多一次！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快拋掉它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別妄想了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎沒法子了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為保守秘密，引爆基地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們仍有很多士兵在基地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管了，國家的機密才最重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我會照命令做的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地...自動爆炸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來，他們是放棄了這裏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦的機動戰士真的這麼利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們亦要把正在試驗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新一批機動戰士投入戰場才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了 我成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯幫軍想全力進攻的ZION基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已被我消滅了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都燒燬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們將所有情報機都破壞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是102採礦基地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第102採礦基地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來...我攻擊的這地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是所有的基地中一個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷比爾將軍要進攻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕非這種小規模據點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是一個更大的礦山...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是過路的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久會有ZION或聯邦的救援隊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耐心等候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已止血了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是訊號鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人來你便用它吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.34,0:21:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.84,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有人來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.84,0:21:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要抱著希望啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.78,0:21:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.15,0:21:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兄弟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.62,0:21:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你是那機動戰士駕駛員的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.79,0:21:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我便真的不敢信的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.13,0:21:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員的心腸太好了很易沒命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說我很易沒命？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.82,0:22:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是訊號彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.17,0:22:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.18,0:22:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠近去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.32,0:22:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·?波 是在附近嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.49,0:22:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.16,0:22:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很利害...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.86,0:22:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一個GUNDAM便破壞成這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另無其它可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.26,0:22:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過似乎不是個大基地 對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.44,0:22:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！否則就不會被一個GUNDAM完全破壞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.11,0:22:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他這樣做只會打草驚蛇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我敢說，敵人一定會更加倍戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅必然\N當正自己是大英雄了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.19,0:22:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們不是正在找他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.32,0:22:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又走了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.82,0:22:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.67,0:22:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼？為甚麼你要走呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.47,0:23:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你不知道我很擔心你的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.95,0:23:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅的眼前看到了交戰的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.60,0:23:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是對White Base進行特攻的拉爾隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.48,0:23:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當趕來的GUNDAM之光束來復槍擊破古夫時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.99,0:23:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.96,0:23:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.39,0:23:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『蘭巴·拉爾特攻』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎

